                        <bibl>B.  Vandenhoff, <title rend="italic">Exegesis Psalmorum, imprimis
                                messianicorum, apud Syros Nestorianos</title> (1899), 13–15 (Syr.),
                            24–6 (<abbr>LT</abbr>).</bibl>
                        <bibl>L.  Van Rompay, <title rend="italic">Théodore de Mopsueste. Fragments
